            "answer_text": "By naming what\u2019s going on and redirecting the discussion back to the actual topic. A straw man argument attempts to reinterpret your argument in a way you never intended and isn\u2019t correct. Don\u2019t respond to it directly \u2014 that only gives it life! It will become a runaway horse with you flailing about wondering what the heck just happened. Whatever you do, don\u2019t go into the light! ",
